## Basic Information


### Naming Convention
$APOGEE_REDUX/[APRED]/visit/[TELESCOPE]/[FIELD]/[PLATE]/[MJD]/apPlateSum-[PLATE]-[MJD].fits

### Releases
WORK

### Enviroments
APOGEE_REDUX

### Approximate Size
351 KB

### File Type
FITS

### Generated by Product
apogee_drp

### Is a VAC
False
